headline: CoStar Group Founder and CEO Andy Florance Featured on Sixth Annual Virginia 500 Power List
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., September 17, 2025--CoStar Group, Inc. (NASDAQ: CSGP), a leading provider of online real estate marketplaces, information, analytics and 3D digital twin technology in the property markets, today announced that Andy Florance, Founder and Chief Executive Officer, was recognized on Virginia Business’ Virginia 500 power list, an annual ranking of the most influential leaders across business, government, real estate and other key sectors in the Commonwealth.
